# Weather API Project

This project provides a REST API to fetch and analyze historical weather data.

## Features
- Process CSV or Excel files via CLI input
- Fetch weather data by:
  - Year
  - Year/Month
  - Year/Month/Day
- Fetch statistics (max, min, median) for:
  - Temperature
  - Humidity
  - Pressure
  - Heat Index
- Pagination support for large datasets
- Validation for month/day input
- Handles missing or empty database gracefully

## File Structure
wether_project/
├── app.py
├── processing.py
├── README.md
├── requirements.txt
├── weather_data.csv
└── weather.db

