## Installation

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
Usage
1️⃣ Process CSV/Excel to Database
bash
Copy code
python processing.py weather_data.csv
# or
python processing.py weather_data.xlsx
2️⃣ Run API
bash
Copy code
python app.py
3️⃣ API Endpoints
Fetch weather data:

sql
Copy code
GET /weather/<year>
GET /weather/<year>/<month>
GET /weather/<year>/<month>/<day>
Fetch stats:

sql
Copy code
GET /weather/stats/<year>/<month>/<day>
Pagination:

pgsql
Copy code
Add ?page=X&limit=Y
Example:

bash
Copy code
/weather/2023/01?page=2&limit=50
Notes
Ensure the database weather.db exists before running API

Valid month: 1–12, valid day: 1–31

